      "This is a SURGICAL EMERGENCY — decompressive laminectomy ideally within 24-48 hours for best neurologic recovery",
      "MRI is the gold standard — EMERGENT MRI, not 'next available'",
      "Bladder scan showing >500mL post-void residual in setting of back pain = cauda equina until proven otherwise",
