          "aiPatientUpdate": "Where am I? Everything hurts... my muscles are so sore. I feel like I ran a marathon.",
          "teaching": "✅ Dantrolene reduces rigidity → reduces heat generation → temperature drops. Continue dantrolene + bromocriptine until symptoms fully resolve. Aggressive fluids for renal protection. When psychiatrically stable, can restart antipsychotic from different class at lowest dose (avoid rechallenge with same agent)."
