          "teaching": "✅ SS vs NMS pearls: SS = clonus + hyperreflexia + agitation (serotonergic drugs). NMS = rigidity + bradykinesia + AMS (antipsychotic drugs). SS resolves faster (24-72h). Discharge when asymptomatic. Avoid serotonergic combinations in future."
