      "Bilateral SDH (check contralateral side on CT — common in elderly)",
      "Coagulopathy contributing to expansion (reverse anticoagulation immediately)",
      "Elder abuse (falls + intracranial hemorrhage — screen per protocol, but this appears accidental)",
      "Spinal cord injury (fall today — assess for concurrent cervical spine injury)"
