      "Not reversing anticoagulation immediately — the SDH will continue to expand while the patient is anticoagulated",
      "Delaying neurosurgery consultation — 11mm midline shift with declining GCS needs emergent evacuation",
      "Not monitoring for herniation — serial neuro checks every 15-30 minutes while awaiting surgery",
