          "examNote": "Pain improved. RUS: wall thickening 5mm, pericholecystic fluid, gallstones. No CBD dilation. Lap chole planned.",
          "aiPatientUpdate": "Pain medicine helped. They said I need surgery?",
          "teaching": "Standard: IVF, abx, pain, NPO, early surgery. RUS diagnostic (>95%). Cholecystectomy within 72h."
