          "teaching": "Acquired C1-INH def: SAME presentation as HAE but (1) adult onset with no family hx (2) C1q LOW (normal in HAE) (3) Associated with lymphoproliferative disease. Treat underlying cause. Acute attacks: same as HAE (C1-INH, icatibant). Higher doses may be needed due to antibody consumption."
